Literature Review
========================================================


- I conducted a literature review for the Environmental Data Center as part of a project with the National Parks Service
- The subject was hurricane impacts and change analysis
that could be applied to Gateway National Recreation Area, Assateague and Fire Island National Seashores. 
- Focused on the methodologies of each study, and did not analyze 
the results
