Reference Managers Cont.
=====
* If you currently use a reference manager and feel comfortable with it, carry on.
* Mendeley 
  * 2 gb of storage space, Pdf import capability, collaborative sharing, social network elements, and free
* Refworks
  * Full web functionality, 150 mb of storage, free through URI
* EndNote
  * 2 gb of storage space, desktop application requires a subscription
  
